+ * expects a texture slot such as GL_TEXTURE0 to reduce chances of
+ * miss-use by the caller.
+ *
+ * The value stored to the uniform is in the form of 0 for GL_TEXTURE0,
+ * 1 for GL_TEXTURE1, and so on.
